{"title":"荐歌：慢灵魂（卢广仲）","slug":"荐歌：慢灵魂（卢广仲）","date":"2022-06-10T10:28:41.000Z","updated":"2022-06-10T10:29:22.801Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/荐歌：慢灵魂（卢广仲）.json","excerpt":"文章来自微信公众号“科文路”，欢迎关注、互动。转发须注明出处。","covers":null,"content":"<blockquote>\n<p>文章来自微信公众号“科文路”，欢迎关注、互动。转发须注明出处。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<iframe frameborder=\"no\" border=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" width=330 height=86 src=\"//music.163.com/outchain/player?type=2&id=109444&auto=1&height=66\"></iframe>\n\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n<p>周末愉快！</p>\n<p>忙碌的工作日间又有了两天放松的机会。惬意的周末配上卢广仲的这首《慢灵魂》再适合不过了~</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E6%85%A2%E7%81%B5%E9%AD%82/5091827\" title=\"百度百科\">百度百科</a>：专辑中的歌曲是卢广仲有感于现代人普遍出现的焦虑感而创作的。卢广仲一直倡导健康生活理念，专辑同名主打歌《慢灵魂》是他为整天忙碌的人所写。他希望通过该曲让听众静下来，找到适合的健康节奏生活。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span class=\"line\">32</span><br><span class=\"line\">33</span><br><span class=\"line\">34</span><br><span class=\"line\">35</span><br><span class=\"line\">36</span><br><span class=\"line\">37</span><br><span class=\"line\">38</span><br><span class=\"line\">39</span><br><span class=\"line\">40</span><br><span class=\"line\">41</span><br><span class=\"line\">42</span><br><span class=\"line\">43</span><br><span class=\"line\">44</span><br><span class=\"line\">45</span><br><span class=\"line\">46</span><br><span class=\"line\">47</span><br><span class=\"line\">48</span><br><span class=\"line\">49</span><br><span class=\"line\">50</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">慢灵魂</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">作词 : 钟成虎</span><br><span class=\"line\">作曲 : 卢广仲</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">晚霞灿烂照着我</span><br><span class=\"line\">一朵蒲公英飘落窗口</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">就在小镇的街头</span><br><span class=\"line\">数着路灯我一个人走</span><br><span class=\"line\">终究会习惯 这种生活</span><br><span class=\"line\">太多的困惑 我不想懂</span><br><span class=\"line\">就在没有月光的时候</span><br><span class=\"line\">流星划过我的身后</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">微风轻轻吹 吹得我心醉</span><br><span class=\"line\">我像风筝飞 被吹得好远</span><br><span class=\"line\">越过了无垠海边 我只想要慢慢飞</span><br><span class=\"line\">微风轻轻吹 谁在流眼泪</span><br><span class=\"line\">我像风筝飞 越过了界限</span><br><span class=\"line\">好远 流星划过的瞬间</span><br><span class=\"line\">我才发现找不到 我的世界</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">点点星光照着我</span><br><span class=\"line\">这种寂寞穿过我胸口</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">就在小镇的街头</span><br><span class=\"line\">数着路灯我一个人走</span><br><span class=\"line\">终究会习惯 这种生活</span><br><span class=\"line\">太多的困惑 我不想懂</span><br><span class=\"line\">就在没有月光的时候</span><br><span class=\"line\">流星划过我的身后</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">微风轻轻吹 吹得我心碎</span><br><span class=\"line\">我像风筝飞 被吹得好远</span><br><span class=\"line\">越过了无垠海边 我只想要慢慢飞</span><br><span class=\"line\">微风轻轻吹 谁在流眼泪</span><br><span class=\"line\">我像风筝飞 越过了界限 好远</span><br><span class=\"line\">流星划过的瞬间</span><br><span class=\"line\">我才发现找不到 我的世界</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">终究会习惯 这种生活</span><br><span class=\"line\">太多的困惑 我不想懂</span><br><span class=\"line\">就在没有月光的时候 流星划过我的身后</span><br><span class=\"line\">微风轻轻吹 吹得我心醉</span><br><span class=\"line\">我像风筝飞 被吹得好远</span><br><span class=\"line\">越过了无垠海边 我只能够慢慢飞</span><br><span class=\"line\">微风轻轻吹 不要流眼泪 我像风筝飞 越过了界限 好远</span><br><span class=\"line\">原谅我的慢灵魂 我担心会找不到</span><br><span class=\"line\">希望找得到 会不会跟不上 你的世界</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><strong>都看到这儿了，不如关注每日推送的“科文路”、互动起来~</strong></p>\n<p><strong>至少点个赞再走吧~</strong></p>\n","more":"<p>周末愉快！</p>\n<p>忙碌的工作日间又有了两天放松的机会。惬意的周末配上卢广仲的这首《慢灵魂》再适合不过了~</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E6%85%A2%E7%81%B5%E9%AD%82/5091827\" title=\"百度百科\">百度百科</a>：专辑中的歌曲是卢广仲有感于现代人普遍出现的焦虑感而创作的。卢广仲一直倡导健康生活理念，专辑同名主打歌《慢灵魂》是他为整天忙碌的人所写。他希望通过该曲让听众静下来，找到适合的健康节奏生活。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"lin